messages.title: My Labour Party pledges to you
messages.content: The only party that will always be here for the many, not just a privileged few.

leaflet.personalStatement: It's time for a fresh start with a young, energetic and local candidate. Time to turn the page on the politics of the past. I will stay true to the values of opportunity and fairness. With your support, we can pave a new way forward together. George Aylett - your future, your candidate for change.

contactInformation.address: The Labour Party, FREEPOST SW8020, Salisbury, SP2 7BR
